    <h1>Information Gain</h1>
    <p class="description">Google's framework for evaluating whether a page adds genuinely new information beyond what competing pages already say. The concept rewards original research and proprietary data — and penalises content that simply repackages what already ranks.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
